{"h30d9d931gbee0g4705gb2fagda9eefc445f4": ["Is the hag gone? Gods, tell me she's gone. Oh, please. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "f4cbaf1c-c1b2-7d72-f512-873070b8b42d"], "hf0038fcag2932g47d6g885cga48c33152893": ["She's dead. You're safe now. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "fc95b1a5-5f64-843f-e8b4-72ef9544196b"], "h03e9b9dbgab59g4169gaf54g861233bd7514": ["May she burn in the Nine Hells. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "40c8540c-c277-691d-ed80-227653be50f8"], "hd89cc56dg4af3g48cagb280g2b50956f82a2": ["The things she did - the things she made me do. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "dc4e5bd2-bb24-986f-20c4-65e095c8387b"], "hcf5f09aegcdfeg4a4dg89beg60ac3615761d": ["Vile, disgusting... ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "3ceb1fe4-060c-7ded-2194-addae5626efb"], "h5c1f7822gf733g4ed0g9b7ag3c61e2535371": ["Good gods...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "22f66fe9-9443-8ebb-97f8-09081458d9a7"], "h959b77d0ge23bg4bbdg9642gdc057f8d1efc": ["You - you're the one. The <i>mind flayer. </i>", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "21da8f50-33e0-35ab-a8ae-66690a348573"], "h8711f87ag075cg4743g8312gc639e742b1b2": ["Not if I can help it. Can you still see it? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "b231356b-c260-92dc-d529-fb065ce03edf"], "hee3ade32g75fcg4c8cg94faga3d7a0941521": ["No - the hag's 'gift' is gone but it's - it's going to happen. Soon.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "75e3dc59-fc0c-5833-fb6e-05700541cc71"], "h3871562ega1ecg4126g9fbag1d6cd017d1fe": ["I saw you screaming - covered in your own insides as that - that <i>thing</i> bursts out of your skull.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "548807f3-a820-9144-23d1-223c0b97c7ed"], "h751e26fbg8401g4bbbga394g7f9d3bf9bc40": ["You change, skin ripping from your body and then you butcher... everyone. Everyone around you. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "3e9bdacc-31af-1258-38c6-37f69c341944"], "h9192bc4fg1b11g4cd2ga841g8fd33b320d63": ["Be specific. When will this happen?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "5f103786-aac9-9ae3-160a-9c69c3b4aac8"], "h0d511a1cg3f68g4ed7gbf3ag3212c678fbc9": ["I - I don't know. It could be a tenday.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "70398ab0-8f80-78c7-f6ed-3a819283c593"], "hb50a2a8fg0a89g4af6ga9bdgb06be6d4d4cc": ["Could be any moment. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "add0201a-aee4-d945-3c76-0d00dab015b4"], "h44a7222dg54fbg4326g9607g97ab3e6a637a": ["I can't do this. You're too dangerous. I'm - I'm sorry. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "031fca9b-5ca5-73b0-4db6-5438fcbd5710"], "h5d27e985g23cbg45beg9fd2ge9b7ba2661b4": ["You're wrong. I'll stop it. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "2f058d5a-34d1-f756-2c12-9a9e18817406"], "h114e120fgfcd1g49edg9cf0g59fc93f97642": ["You can't. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "4eee0ac6-c88f-5088-137d-5823fe8d09aa"], "hfa2a07dfg9916g4941g98f6g1e1f5246a5f2": ["I'm so sorry. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "6824c7dc-ea52-3c0c-7ae0-86a09c11262d"], "hae8ecf7eg763fg4b1cg830fg06f4b80afd0c": ["I butcher everyone? That sounds <i>delightful</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "a525954f-ac12-f967-c15c-92d791aaa5c4"], "hcf0b4e18gae14g4228gb861g5b9e8123aa4e": ["Hells. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "edefe6e9-8ddf-02ae-2732-473a3ab8f76b"], "h5b237926ge9c6g494dga9b9g63813070c174": ["Death can't come quick enough for you - <i>monster. </i>", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "9ab45b26-e5c1-1572-a6e8-9f5d32c745d5"], "ha3f02ce8g5bbbg4aa9g8926g5ccf62992e65": ["I have no idea what you're talking about. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "9f59a257-b1be-520f-487b-549f96334f8c"], "h9bb54e93g4df7g40ccg90b6ge3e6bb93f58f": ["No. I <i>saw </i>it. You're covered in blood and gore - vomiting. And then... your skull splits open.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "7077f0ba-fe9f-d348-aa7d-1f5c0cf9e41e"], "h6f34baa6g5bb6g4158ga043g4a61d135fa3a": ["That thing bursts out of you and you're - you're screaming.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "e6785250-690f-a62c-30c8-ad493ff78e29"], "ha3f9e385g1516g4ef1g9528gb22395097353": ["I still hear it. Still see your eyes go dead, and you... you butcher them. Everyone around you. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "3e5ee432-8248-5cec-68c7-53bd32bda824"], "ha50b8369gc8e3g400cg9737gb4b00efd7a11": ["Why should I trust you? Or the hag's magic?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "ff054769-1ddb-3808-02e3-90036961e728"], "hd9176ee3g6932g4fbcg9f48gf7c38d4cd20c": ["Hag magic it might be, but it's never been wrong. Not once. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "29ef1c57-2043-fc78-2abf-5c063ea12f94"], "h707f4a7dg85d3g4663g9279gb4ee1f0e9b03": ["I'm so sorry. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "3a8b07e2-040b-8d87-eaf2-eb00152f9963"], "hdd905ed3g387fg4ed6gbf94ga1e21e72716f": ["I can't stay. You're too dangerous. But I hope... I only hope it's a quick death.  ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "417fd477-d69c-0458-973c-4ea11a9f9640"], "hb819c86eg335bg4f21ga8d1gaead20692914": ["I saved your life. Be grateful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "49e1793c-8d24-fd64-e6d1-e0d239157293"], "h63a6bea3g04f7g4053gb658g98cb34fdf0a9": ["No. You don't understand. You <i>kill </i>them. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "00194aaf-1b9e-02f3-6f53-e2faaf65991f"], "h2ddb14e2g3c95g4fb2gb379g183e379e94f8": ["Say that again, and I'll rip your throat out with my teeth.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "f2285923-b681-55bb-b56a-4bab8bb4bada"], "h572b9850g6bebg4ffcg9063gf5c3c594e013": ["Shut your damn mouth. And <i>never </i>call me that again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "9236874f-5229-b457-57c5-086064c43b6e"], "h79d76c6ag4c4eg4400gba76g0941d7f7625d": ["She's gone. You're safe now. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "e251010e-28de-c5fc-06be-daa7b6b4e701"], "h4cd69306g754ag4374gb6b7g8666c193ae0a": ["You're lucky to be alive. I could have killed you. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "b6c009a0-2810-98d4-573b-11e6b36dec7d"], "hba0e0264g3f77g4ffdg9c91g68537cbd7ae9": ["That damn shrew would have loved it. Would have loved watching you murder me. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "fecfded9-14e4-be1f-1404-ca157e71f4de"], "hce58beb7ga095g4b24g8d1egbca617f4442c": ["Are you all right? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "88d69b87-aa67-8fa3-72aa-6f3b8d32aa20"], "ha9e9170ag79cbg41a6g9249gd1b7f508d892": ["No. Not even a little bit. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "89f29ce6-4f71-9a23-16a0-197e358d79e9"], "he12abae6g3172g479cg8ef7g8a5ee7064bb1": ["The hag - there's never been a more vile creature.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "4e8eb70c-c2cf-4fdc-b429-7c6a4f239384"], "heb675ef9gb0a9g4670g9975g29b0d26030cf": ["The things she did to me - the things she made me do I... ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "7f49fdd8-3e86-2523-23f7-571361b960ba"], "h5e008e53gc6f1g4510ga1c2gc49f1fb21668": ["She's dead. You're safe now. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "6b825ece-606d-9d4d-5ea3-5a957ac1f4c0"], "h3327e0ffg46d2g4a89ga4d6g8bb2c8819aac": ["The hag - there's never been a more vile creature. The things she did to me...", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "6f501b27-9b90-697f-08b5-bcc602a034f6"], "hb9ef8884g73e7g4f3cgb0f5gcf1fa0c8b26f": ["She's gone. You're safe now. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "7db67837-a21e-8c74-8ca0-32b6c1bfaef6"], "hfc1007f7g1010g4ba2gaf37g87f4722a653d": ["Why were you even here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "6225fe39-0ad7-a0d7-6ecb-b77b9fe6513e"], "h91741326g0469g4bc9gbef4gb7472d5ce5d4": ["I was a fool. I wanted to know my fate. I had a choice between two lives, and I was frightened of choosing wrong.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "62a86515-3f80-ab2b-4927-554797634fa6"], "h35dcbcf0gb20cg4364g851dg9f40a9a660c5": ["I asked the hag to help me see what the future would hold. Got what I wished for, too.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "ca8fcf90-891b-4edb-92ad-d75634f5c730"], "he2c2d479gbcadg4abcg8adag8c47d39eba45": ["I saw my future self - a corpse, rotten with maggots. And everyone around me dead. Putrid and dead.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "211da9ef-63cd-745c-c153-7fe9872be75a"], "h712d08a2g27c0g4e16gbb6bga78edda43ff1": ["You mentioned choosing between two lives. What were they? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "9676b9a9-afc7-dce9-e03c-abcf8bce2151"], "h4417b61fg91c6g4cdeg824cg9b7fee075e89": ["A boring story. Stay or go. Marriage and kids or a life of novelty.", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "25ae0e16-76cb-7f82-016f-757b96d803f8"], "h9636a882g3c64g4d67gb388gd5f4228e177d": ["I lost my best years rather than just... <i>choose.</i>", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "15024880-b798-a1e9-6030-38a34606fa70"], "h06f4ea09g9e2dg4e02gb2ebg4d562b0fd136": ["Leave while you can - and be careful. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "f79b766c-44a3-019e-786c-9ed596311a9c"], "hfef956d3g9ffeg48ffg96cag0dde10d0006f": ["Get out of here. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "a6fe5627-2fd2-7275-9fb7-b41e70815d83"], "h825d398dg2b5dg46c9g8593g7a1fa39efce4": ["Yes. I will. <i>Thank you.</i>", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "a25fcf5d-364f-f05e-3d2d-9a6e0106ee02"], "h14d3cba5gc850g485fga8cdg462237f9f2f7": ["Leave <i>darthiir</i> - before I finished what the hag started.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "d2a6a979-dc52-0616-fb99-a2347e1a3b43"], "h191f8a8cgbb1eg437bga51eg1783b36cecb2": ["Yes. I will. Forgive me. ", "4c1e4973-e9e8-458c-bd77-0a8b9ef7e3bf", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_003_Freed.html", "e1f54698-5600-16b4-381d-dd75105259ad"]}